net.proteusframework.internet.http.useragent

Class UserAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.internet.http.useragent.UserAgent

  • public final class UserAgent
extends Object
    UserAgent parser.

    This class should *not* be used to determine generated HTML pages or Javascript. An example of a good use for this class is HTTP header output or generating statistics.

    see http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc1945.html
    see http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc2068.html
    see http://www.pgts.com.au/pgtsj/pgtsj0212d.html
    Author:
    Russell Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
